{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT's strengths and weaknesses were shown in its application in STEM learning.",
    "Users shared it was a great help in learning computer science subjects,\" I've been using ChatGPT to help me write code for new concepts but I prioritize 2 main constraints.",
    "(1) I rewrite the entire code and explain it to myself.",
    "(2) if I don't understand or know something I ask it to explain it….",
    "On the other hand, another user pointed out its weakness in simple statistics \"The way ChatGPT works makes it very good at writing things like prose and lengthy exam answers, but not so good at solving even simple math problems\"."
  ]
}